# Project Overview

This is a modern web application built with Astro and UnoCSS. Here are the key files and directories:

- [astro.config.mjs](mdc:astro.config.mjs) - Astro configuration
- [uno.config.ts](mdc:uno.config.ts) - UnoCSS configuration and theme settings
- [src/](mdc:src) - Main source code directory
- [public/](mdc:public) - Static assets

## Key Configuration Files
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [postcss.config.cjs](mdc:postcss.config.cjs) - PostCSS configuration
- [svelte.config.js](mdc:svelte.config.js) - Svelte configuration

